            <title><![CDATA[【[抓狂]没必要太焦虑！#医生教你自测腺样体肥大#】#腺样体面容自测# 医生提醒，腺样体的问题需要重视，但没必要去夸大它。很多家长晚上不敢睡觉，天天扒孩子嘴...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[抓狂]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_zhuakuang-c007ffb7fe.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>没必要太焦虑！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%E8%85%BA%E6%A0%B7%E4%BD%93%E8%82%A5%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%E8%85%BA%E6%A0%B7%E4%BD%93%E8%82%A5%E5%A4%A7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生教你自测腺样体肥大#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%85%BA%E6%A0%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%85%BA%E6%A0%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E8%87%AA%E6%B5%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#腺样体面容自测#</span></a> 医生提醒，腺样体的问题需要重视，但没必要去夸大它。很多家长晚上不敢睡觉，天天扒孩子嘴巴，有的家长还担心孩子是不是打呼噜不喘气了。医生表示，虽然孩子有点打呼噜或者张嘴睡觉，但不会缺氧。回家可以这样给小朋友测试下：把嘴巴闭上，手指头放到鼻子前面然后吸气，再用鼻子往手指上喷气，如果有气流，说明问题不大。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%85%BA%E6%A0%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#腺样体面容#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4894440553381891" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly1hdbzuivoy6j60hs0a0t9n02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/rr8AE51hlx084WAhmNsQ010412006uMV0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682486359&amp;ssig=0kCevtwOg%2B&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/haceTE9tlx084WAhgZx6010412005OZU0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1682486359&amp;ssig=EBV%2Bwdr24F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4894440553381891&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
